# API route rules

- Validate request bodies with Zod; return 400 with structured errors
- Persist runs only via `lib/store.ts` — no raw `@vercel/kv` puts
- Include `runId` in logs and error responses where applicable
- Workflow-triggering routes use Node.js runtime (not Edge) when Workflow SDK is involved
- Contract tests in `app/api/**/*.contract.test.ts` — mock KV when storage is not under test
